ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/157714/', '', 'Ethchlorvynol, Tropicamide, Phenylephrine', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole, Tetracaine, Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Nitrous acid, More', 1767369485);
